                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10095" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0301</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">420 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">药明康德：股份回购筑起投资者的“防波堤”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">WuXi AppTec: Share buybacks build a &#39;breakwater&#39; for investors</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">冯文红，刘本湘，陈晓晓，王丽洁，姜咏彤，王子怡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湘潭大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无锡药明康德新药开发股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股份回购；投资者保护；股本优化；回购注销</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Share repurchase;Repurchase and cancellation;Equity optimization; Investor protection</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股份回购是稳定股价、恢复市场信心的常用有效工具。作为中国生物医药研发服务领域的领军企业，药明康德在2024年面临美国《生物安全法案》引发的市场动荡以及新“国九条”政策中对投资者权益保护要求升级的双重压力，通过股份回购注销机制实现股价回升与重拾投资者信心成为公司的核心议题。本案例聚焦药明康德2024年的三次股份回购事件，主要以其股价变化、股东结构变动等数据，并辅以相关财务指标，探讨公司如何通过“三轮驱动+四维加固”的动态策略应对外部政策冲击，实现投资者保护。本案例旨在为生物医药行业在国际监管趋严与资本市场波动加剧的复杂环境下，优化治理结构、强化风险抵御能力提供可借鉴的管理框架，同时为政策制定者完善上市公司投资者保护制度提供参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Share repurchases are a common and effective tool for stabilizing stock prices and restoring market confidence. As a leading enterprise in China&#39;s biopharmaceutical research and development services sector, WuXi AppTec faced dual pressures in 2024 from market turmoil caused by the US Biological Security Act and the upgraded requirements for investor protection in the new &quot;Nine-Point Plan&quot; policy. Realizing a stock price recovery and regaining investor confidence through the share repurchase cancellation mechanism became the company&#39;s core issue. This case focuses on WuXi AppTec&#39;s three share repurchase events in 2024, mainly using data such as changes in stock prices and shareholder structure, supplemented by relevant financial indicators, to explore how the company responded to external policy shocks and achieved investor protection through a dynamic strategy of &quot;three-wheel drive + four-dimensional reinforcement&quot;. This case aims to provide a management framework for the biopharmaceutical industry to optimize governance structure and strengthen risk resistance in the complex environment of tightening international regulation and capital market volatility, and also provide a reference for policymakers to improve the investor protection system for listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股份回购；投资者保护；股份回购与投资者保护的关系；信号理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
